#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:7
msgid "Developing Python Plugins"
msgstr "Razvoj Python dodataka"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:17
msgid ""
"It is possible to create plugins in the Python programming language. In "
"comparison with classical plugins written in C++ these should be easier to "
"write, understand, maintain and distribute due to the dynamic nature of the "
"Python language."
msgstr ""
"Moguće je praviti dodatke u programskom jeziku Python. U poređenju sa "
"klasičnim dodacima pisanim u C++-u, ove bi trebalo da bude lakše pisati, "
"razumeti, održavati i distribuirati zbog dinamičke prirode jezika Python."

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:22
msgid ""
"Python plugins are listed together with C++ plugins in QGIS plugin manager. "
"They are searched for in :file:`~/(UserProfile)/python/plugins` and these "
"paths:"
msgstr ""
"Python dodaci se navode zajedno sa C++ dodacima u QGIS menadžeru dodataka. "
"Traže se u :file:`~/(UserProfile)/python/plugins` i na sledećim putanjama:"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:25
msgid "UNIX/Mac: :file:`(qgis_prefix)/share/qgis/python/plugins`"
msgstr "UNIX/Mac: :file:`(qgis_prefix)/share/qgis/python/plugins`"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:26
msgid "Windows: :file:`(qgis_prefix)/python/plugins`"
msgstr "Windows: :file:`(qgis_prefix)/python/plugins`"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:28
msgid ""
"For definitions of ``~`` and ``(UserProfile)`` see "
":ref:`core_and_external_plugins`."
msgstr ""
"Za definicije ``~`` i ``(UserProfile)`` pogledajte "
":ref:`core_and_external_plugins`."

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/plugins/index.rst:32
msgid ""
"By setting `QGIS_PLUGINPATH` to an existing directory path, you can add this"
" path to the list of paths that are searched for plugins."
msgstr ""
"Postavljanjem `QGIS_PLUGINPATH` na putanju postojećeg direktorijuma, možete "
"dodati tu putanju u listu putanja na kojima se traže dodaci."
